  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">A Home To Build Futures In Medellin, Colombia</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Cultivando Sonrisas provides a safe home for girls (ages 0-18), who are at risk of physical and sexual abuse, and exploitation in Medellin, Colombia. For 6 years we have rented a home, but now we must move from that home. The GOAL is to buy a property so the girls and the foundation have a permanent safe place to call home. This project will allow us to buy a home with lots of space, where the girls can run, play and grow, while dreaming of their bright futures that are now in sight!</narrative>
  </description>
